You go straight off the halas ramp dont make any turns untill you come to a wide open space with some igloos when you reach tthis point go to the upper left hand corner of this circular area then take that path... once on the path take the first left you can and go straight on that... this is where i start to forget but im pretty sure you can go straight but you may have to bear left at one point (i forget) you then should eventually reach a place where there are trees and rocks stay there and he should be there or be walking around... I understand these directions are probably very hard to understand but its the best i can do hope these help somewhat
